|---------|---------|
| **Failure case** | Prompt/tool injection → exfiltration, lateral movement, destructive infra calls. |
| **Root cause** | Agents treated as trusted users; static API keys; no runtime policy on tool args. |
| **Strategy** | MCP/tool gateway; JIT ephemeral credentials; OPA/Cedar (or equivalent) policy-as-code; input/output guardrails; mandatory totem on high-blast-radius calls. |
| **10-year maintenance** | Policies in Git; semver; breaking-change review; immutable audit store; replayable incident bundles. |

